werkzeug==3.1.0

# Transitive native deps forced up to their lowest Python 3.13 (cp313) wheel
# release. At their previous resolved versions these had no cp313 wheel, so the
# slim image would build lz4 from source (fails: no compiler) and silently drop
# google-crc32c/markupsafe to their pure-python fallbacks (losing the native
# acceleration the 3.12 image shipped).
